{"tid":1433472,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"醫生真心係天使（真人真事冇改編）","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:31:09.000Z","uid":203885,"like":83,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"25c9a567f6bdd91279c23954f16a54ebc1451e0a","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"話說小弟最近出街都食得太多二手煙，太多塵，個肺今日又唔舒服，就諗住去睇醫生。去左間私家診所睇肺，對話大概內容如下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：醫生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日有啲咩唔舒服呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日放工個時突然Felel到條氣唔順；唔知係咪呢2日有颱風，而且小弟又曾經有呼吸道舊患。依家吸大啖氣就會胸悶又有嘢壓住咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你最近有冇去食煙呀？（食彈）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：最近都有嘅，不過應該唔關事掛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁呀，咁你又有舊患，你洗唔洗要支噴藥？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係哮喘藥呀？係咪有類固醇個隻？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔係，只係支呼吸道擴張嘅藥，冇類固醇架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁呀，好，我要一支啦，不過呢支幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔洗錢！你有冇食煙朋友要用呀，我仲有幾盒呀，我攞出黎比你啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下，我唔好意思攞，唔要啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔緊要啦，最重要你地冇事。同埋依家啲電視台淨係會影個啲打交，掉磚，放火個啲片，你地盡量唔好做啦，我支持你地，但呢啲行為會比啲市民負面形象，<br />\n咁成功就會難上加難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（眼濕濕）多謝你，我唔會放火架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁不如你攞幾支走，送比你啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：多謝你，感激！多謝，多謝，多謝...（因為除咗多謝唸唔到其他adj.）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：記得啦，千其唔好有事呀！我地，特別係屋企人會擔心你地架！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好多謝你醫生！（handshaking）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：加油，唔洗客氣！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走出房門就即刻喊咗出黎。<br />\n<br />\n小弟最後攞左3支salbutamol sulfate<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當心有啲對話冇咁重要就省略咗。<br />\n<br />\n係呢到，小弟都想講2句。<br />\n<br />\n希望去前線發夢嘅隊友/手足 真係可以忍下手，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡量唔好放火</span></span>。雖然小弟認為有部份原因係想泄憤又或者想call消防令到班狗碌黎碌去。但係我地仲有好多方法係街撚狗，e.g報下案，等報案室忙下；做下街坊去撩興啲狗；掉下啲雞蛋；又或者啲觀星筆又可以自己較下電阻，觀星要強啲嘅光先睇得靚啲架嘛。(Youtube有tutorialssssssss)<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地一直要捉緊軸心，保持冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、立即實行雙真普選</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n即使我有意見，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">但一定會<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟咩都唔識，亂唸ideas。<br />\n<br />\nS f 1999"},{"pid":"a6c52431d7279266b2bd2dae940f50796e5bc1f6","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6f4bcf4c07e5450fa09232875bf27212bdc158","tid":1433472,"uid":301839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"f5ccbf68399b5953d8485841928fa5dc8f6e179e","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203da34a6d510d4bdadf69d6378acc7f317f9b36","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79064cc971bdfb11308d17bba7603f548a35130","tid":1433472,"uid":241239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"喊撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172844b54d6aa90f835fde79aee89859ff042033","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a913d630517f1af90fb0589ca34722626798e1ce","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab33ba5a158a3e272aff4cadcc576cd56daf545","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68470b03c4f215021c1729d19b49c37b6f586290","tid":1433472,"uid":203885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"